Subject: Secunia Research: Adobe Shockwave Player Four
	Integer Overflow Vulnerabilities

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 20/01/2010

  - Adobe Shockwave Player Four Integer Overflow Vulnerabilities -

====================================================================== 
